room_title: Escape room "Cabin Fever" by Project Panic Houston in Houston
room_address: 3510 Main St. Ste C Houston, TX 77002
room_description: A fierce blizzard has hit your secluded ski resort! Caught in the snow, you and your friends were forced to take shelter in a nearby cabin. But beware! The old wooden structure can only stand the brunt of the storm for so long. Can you find a way to save yourself and your companions? Or, will you succumb to the fury of the blizzard?
